\frac{\partial}{\partial r}\int_{\partial B_r(P)} h_R \leq \int_{\partial B_p(r)} \frac{\partial}{\partial r} h_R  +  \int_{\partial B_r(p)} h_R  \frac{\partial}{\partial r} J dr\wedge d\theta
 \leq     \int_{\partial B_p(r)} \frac{\partial}{\partial r} h_R  +  \int_{\partial B_r(p)} h_R H J dr\wedge d\theta 
\leq   \int_{\partial B_p(r)} \frac{\partial}{\partial r} h_R  +  \frac{n-1}{r} \int_{\partial B_r(p)} h_R 
